      "parameters": {
        "content": "## Email to Airtable Automation\nAutomate a workflow that:\n\n✅ Converts **rich text content** from incoming emails to **Markdown**\n✅ Saves the converted Markdown into an **Airtable database**\n\n\n\n\nGmail:\nThe email used for this is flag13302@gmail.com\n\n\nAirtable:\nThe account is used for Airtable is usman.ak508@gmail.com\n\n\n1️⃣ **Trigger: Gmail New Email**\n* Set trigger to:\nEmail received\n\n\n\n2️⃣ **Extract Rich Text Content**\n\nemail body (HTML or rich text)\n\n3️⃣ **Convert to Markdown**\n\n* Use a parser (available in most automation platforms or custom code) to convert:\n\n* Insert new record:\n\nEmail Subject → Airtable Field\nSender Email → Airtable Field\nMarkdown Content → Airtable Long Text Field\n",
        "height": 180,
